  <data name="label2.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Our DelphiGEN allows the users to generate test data suitable for their testing needs. Be it generic data like e mails and passwords or LLM powered,more context oriented data extracted from a chosen website. You are also free to enable or disable the usage of LLM in your generic test data creation.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="label3.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Our ArgosQA allows users to generate edge test cases suitable for webpage testing. You are free to generate from real cases that can be used by gan to create new cases, use LLM to introduce LLM generated cases to seqgan to improve their diversity and lastly use our LLM powered contextual case creation for testing any webpage with forms using the cases tailored directly for that web form.</value>
  </data>
